data.description: Welcome to this newly built, stunning ranch-style home nestled in The Estates Of Hartwood in Stafford County. This exquisite property offers 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms on a generous and level 4-acre lot that balances the comfort of privacy with the convenience of being just miles from downtown.   Step inside to be immersed in the open floorplan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, formal dining room, and living areas - making it ideal for hosting gatherings. The spacious and airy kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with stainless steel appliances, a built-in microwave, gas cooktop, dishwasher, and a wall oven. This gourmet kitchen also features a large island and a butler's pantry, perfect for entertaining family and guests.   Relax and unwind in the cozy living room, complete with a gas fireplace and vaulted ceiling that also serves as the central hub to all other areas of the main floor, including the dry bar connecting it to the formal dining room. Opposite the living area you’ll find a morning room with wall to wall windows and built in benches extending the full length of the room. Step outside to enjoy the deck, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or hosting outdoor gatherings. When it’s time to get some work done, open the French doors just off the main area to your personal home office, complete with built in, wall to wall shelving and cabinetry that will be the envy of your co-workers on your next video call!   Retreat to the primary suite, which includes a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with a spacious stand up shower and oversized soaking tub looking out over the private, wooded property below.   Slip downstairs to a beautifully finished basement consisting of a massive and fully open rec area, two bonus rooms perfect for an office and media/theater room, as well as a large bedroom with its own access to the full bathroom on the level. This space can support a dining area, games and toys, and a spacious sitting/tv area, all with room to spare!   Additional highlights include a 3-car garage, central heating and cooling, a tankless water heater, water softener, and main-level laundry/mud room combination with built shelving and bench for added convenience.   The property is in excellent condition and provides a serene and upscale living experience, with construction completed in 2022 by renowned Atlantic Builders.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. Schedule a showing today and let this exquisite ranch-style home welcome you with its elegance and comfort.
